query:
UPDATE product_categories pc
INNER JOIN products p ON pc.productId = p.id
SET pc.categoryId = 13
WHERE pc.categoryId = 5
AND (
  p.name LIKE '%Vial%' OR
  p.name LIKE '%vial%' OR
  p.name LIKE '%Cap%' OR
  p.name LIKE '%cap%' OR
  p.name LIKE '%Septa%' OR
  p.name LIKE '%septa%'
);
